column1: Baby Barnaby's////Baby Barnaby's channels this low-key
column2: throwback Hawaiian cafe vibe. The inside reminds me of old school 808 with the pretty striped ceiling and old school table tops. A small building with limited seating
column3: you can bet that this place has a killer wait on the weekends. (Seeing as a waitlist is not my strongest point
column4: I'll be there a few minutes before they even open
